OL,5,CWAS IT WRONG TO FEED THE BIRDS?        
OL,7, A pensioner was told this week she will
OL,8, beCjailed for three monthsGif she feeds
OL,9, birds or animals in her garden.        
OL,11, A judge had previously toldCBarbara    
OL,12,CSimpson,G60, she could put food on her 
OL,13, giant 24sq ft bird table but nowhere   
OL,14, else. She broke the ruling and fed     
OL,15, birds elsewhere in her garden.         
OL,17, Go Green takes a look at the issues    
OL,18,Gbehind theCWinchester Crown CourtGand  
OL,19, asks what viewers think.....           
