OL,5,CWAS IT WRONG TO FEED THE BIRDS?        
OL,7, Barbara Simpson began feeding birds    
OL,8, 15-years-ago whenCa sick baby blackbird
OL,9,Glanded on her doorstep and "asked" for 
OL,10, help.                                  
OL,12, She broke an order preventing her from 
OL,13, feeding birds apart from on her bird   
OL,14, table.                                 
OL,16, As the birds came down to feed, she    
OL,17, claims neighboursCbanged blocks of wood
OL,18,Ctogether,G"which frightened the birds  
OL,19, getting the food from the table".      
