OL,5,CWAS IT WRONG TO FEED THE BIRDS?        
OL,7, Barbara Simpson was appearing at court 
OL,8, for the fourth time sinceCWeymouth and 
OL,9,CPortland CouncilGasked a judge to jail 
OL,10, her for breaking an injunction,        
OL,11, forbidding her from feeding the birds. 
OL,13, Neighbours claimed she was spending up 
OL,14, toC#100-a-week feeding birds,Gand urged
OL,15, the council to act.                    
OL,17, After an earlier hearing, Mrs Simpson  
OL,18, said:C"I'm prepared to go to jailGif   
OL,19, they stop me feeding my birds."        
