OL,5,CWAS IT WRONG TO FEED THE BIRDS?        
OL,7, Neighbours opposing Barbara Simpson's  
OL,8, "love of birds" said that cheese, nuts 
OL,9, and seed lay up toCsix inches deepGin  
OL,10, her garden.                            
OL,12, Hundreds of pigeons would gather in    
OL,13, nearby trees,Cwaking them up at 5am,G  
OL,14,Gand soiling their washing and windows. 
OL,16, Winchester Crown Court sentenced Ms    
OL,17, Simpson to aCthree-month suspended jail
OL,18,Cterm,Gon condition she doesn't feed    
OL,19, birds on her lawn or bird-table.       
