OL,5,CWAS IT WRONG TO FEED THE BIRDS?        
OL,6,G                                       
OL,7,GGo Green viewer,CJanet Holden, 37,Gof  
OL,8,CFulham,Gsays she loves birds but if    
OL,9,Gfeeding them presents a nuisance to    
OL,10,Gneighbours, it should be banned.       
OL,11,G                                       
OL,12,G"How would you feel if your neighbour  
OL,13,Gwere attractingCswarms of birdsGlike   
OL,14,Gpigeons to your neighbourhood?         
OL,15,G                                       
OL,16,G"They might be lovely but in large     
OL,17,Gnumbers they're a nightmare - what with
OL,18,Gall their droppings - which they take  
OL,19,Gpleasure inCdropping at random."       
