OL,5,CWAS IT WRONG TO FEED THE BIRDS?        
OL,7,CMaureen Wilmott, 45,GfromCOxford,Gsays 
OL,8,GWinchester Crown Court was right to    
OL,9,Gprevent Barbara Simpson feeding birds  
OL,10,Gin her garden.                         
OL,11,G                                       
OL,12,GShe claims: "Birds, like pigeons, can  
OL,13,Gbe a danger to health. I feel sorry for
OL,14,Gthe woman, but youCcan't let sorrow get
OL,15,Cin the way of practical decisions."    
OL,16,G                                       
OL,17,GHowever,CAnne Hudson, 19,Gof Chelsea,  
OL,18,Gdisagrees: "You should be able to do as
OL,19,Gyou like in your garden!"              
